strings: <se_low>January: It was my first time ever climbing a mountain!
<se_high>Accuracy: We believe we are at the top. And when he comes, I will have to fight Zeman!<page>Accuracy: Act now!
<se_def>China: If I had known that it would be so difficult, I would not have rushed to save this chicken.
<se_def>China: ... well, that is silly, no, that is serious.
<se_high>Dye: you are still hungry it is not necessary. Take off your socks now!
<se_low>It's Maurice.: Hoo! Young people get bored easily. Don't eat mozzarella! It's good to continue every night!
